{"tid":2462371,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"女神IU仙氣漫出！新專輯MV四大情境辣翻　集可愛性感剽悍一身","createTime":"2021-03-26T03:26:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T14:37:04.000Z","uid":9573,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8b1091ff461e9a2feee4333e8b326dd25f0b77","tid":2462371,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:26:10.000Z","msg":"不論演戲唱歌，都深受廣大粉絲喜愛的韓國女神IU李知恩，近年大多以戲劇作品為主，專輯部分則是相隔四年終於推出第五張正規專輯，《LILAC》，而首波主打則是同名的歌曲「LILAC」，MV出爐也等於正式告訴所有粉絲，IU要以歌手的身份再次登上舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/26/3082545-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F26%2F3082545-PH.jpg&h=f8d89416&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼ ▲ IU推出新專輯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/26/3082546-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F26%2F3082546-PH.jpg&h=613af217&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v7bnOxV4jAc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv7bnOxV4jAc&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=fba1c091\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v7bnOxV4jAc</a><br />\n<br />\n在「LILAC」的MV裡，IU先是在車站等車，復古場景和造型，直接點出了IU特有的古典美，而後還有火車過山洞，列車包廂瞬間又變成了小型夜店，IU則換上了較為性感火辣的洋裝，而後又像是嘉年華般的派對，還有一段是IU化身成功夫女打仔，和不少來勢洶洶的男子對打。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/26/3082544-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F26%2F3082544-PH.jpg&h=39564bd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼ ▲ IU在新歌MV上演全武行。<br />\n<br />\n一條列車卻有不同的情境和變化，似乎也像是IU在訴說自己的生活和心境，而喧鬧完的沈澱，又回到了最開始的車站，燈光已暗，人去樓空，議價後以2.5萬租出，呎租42.1元。原本失落的臉，卻又突然來了一班列車，極亮的車燈光線打照在IU臉上，似乎又有什麼新的想法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0-q1KafFCLU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0-q1KafFCLU&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GpmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=ea401f68\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0-q1KafFCLU</a><br />\n<br />\n睽違四年才出新專輯，IU宣傳期也是拉長陣線，從今年一月就先丟出一首新歌「Celebrity」，歌詞裡藏了不少彩蛋，要讓粉絲好好的「仔細聽」，而這彩蛋其實就是IU出道十二年來的點滴心情，都放進了歌詞中，想要透過這樣的方式，來和粉絲互動，造型部分也是相當有誠意，簡直像是「德魯納酒店」的精華版，短短幾分鐘內，IU就連換了七套服裝。"},{"pid":"7d2c6e935abb480ce91dd035aaa336f23c05def0","tid":2462371,"uid":916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"2.5萬租IU<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fa454aa2690d6436521804c6f8288df6199a567","tid":2462371,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"今次咁短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dac15462ea256c0cfe28f3eb5044f85e28c5279e","tid":2462371,"uid":78856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"冇朱千雪既"},{"pid":"fe8a6cdbe98314365a65886e69c33302d1fdef15","tid":2462371,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T14:37:04.000Z","msg":"而喧鬧完的沈澱，又回到了最開始的車站，燈光已暗，人去樓空，議價後以2.5萬租出，呎租42.1元。<br />\n<br />\n又接得幾順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}